The author was born in Kardzhali, Bulgaria in 1989. He is graduated from Trakya University, Faculty of Science, Department of Mathematics in 2012. He is graduated from Master of Science in Finance from the University of the West Of the West of England, Bristol, United Kingdom.In 2015 he started PhD in Economics and Finance in Istanbul Gelisim University, Istanbul, Turkey. The author has two books; "Banking Approach of Banking Customers in Turkey" and "Corporate Social Responsibility and its Contributions."He is still Senior Lecturer in Istanbul Gelisim University, Department of Banking and Insurance. He is married, and speaks English well.
