A visitor for Luca +CD (Vera the Alien Hunter 3)
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=1183738&isWatermarked=true
2016-05-03
 70,12
Vera the Alien Hunter is a fun-to-read set of comic readers offering key English learning skills. Readers will find themselves learning new vocabulary, experiencing important grammar structures in a natural context, and sharpening their reading skills all while having fun reading exciting stories. Vera the Alien Hunter readers are written especially for EFL/ESL learners with the goal of making reading fun. This series of graded readers contains three levels, each with six volumes for preA1-A1 EFL/ESL learners. Vera the Alien Hunter is a new and exciting series of fun-to-read comic readers about Vera and her mysterious cat, Luca. Together they try to protect Earth from invading aliens. With “Vera the Alien Hunter”, students will tag along with Vera as she sets out to save planet Earth from doom. Fun and engaging stories that motivate students to readColorful illustrations that aid comprehensionReading fluency activities to improve reading skills and build confidenceA verity of activities to reinforce speakingGraded grammar focus required for elementary level learnersVocabulary building, listening, and grammar activitiesAudio CD for students to practice listening and speaking Theme songStory with animated voice actors and vivid sound effectsListen and repeat the storyKey words and useful expressionsMobile application to support key vocabulary acquisition
